name: Howling Mad Murdock
description: Captain H. M. "Howling Mad" Murdock is a fictional character and one of the four protagonists of the 1980s action-adventure television series The A-Team.Black and white digital sketch. Made for Inktober 2019 on Ibis Paint X on a Samsung Galaxy Tab S3. 2048 x 2048 @350 dpi.
